metadata.name: CuddlySalmon - Dual Horizons
metadata.description:
"Dual Horizons" is a groundbreaking artwork that blurs the lines between the digital and physical realms, challenging viewers to reconsider their perception of reality. When experienced through a VR headset, "Dual Horizons" transforms into an immersive 360ยบ panorama.

Bridging the gap between the physical and digital worlds, CuddlySalmon crafts mesmerizing AI art experiences that captivate the senses across multiple dimensions.
